Problem Link : 
https://codeforces.com/contest/1207/problem/C

Solution Link : 
https://codeforces.com/contest/1207/submission/102530979

Hint :

[x , x+1]  we are working on an interval.

2 important invalid cases.
1. s[id-1] == '1' and cur_status = 0. 
piller id-1 wants height - 2. [id -1 , id] -> height must be 2.

2. s[id] = 1 , cur_status = 0  -> invalid.
